Medical Expenses Prediction (Linear Regression)

This project uses Linear Regression to predict medical charges for non-smokers based on their age, BMI, and number of children.

The dataset is loaded from expenses.csv, filtered to only non-smokers, and a regression model is trained to estimate charges. The predictions are evaluated using RMSE (Root Mean Square Error) and visualized with Matplotlib and Seaborn.

